# Pancakes

Classic #american #breakfast.

## Dry ingredients

1. Whisk dry ingredients together in a bowl

- all-purpose flour |  300 grams | 
- granulated sugar | 62g | 
- salt | 4g | 
- baking soda | 1g | 
- baking powder | 12g | 
- butter | 21 g | unsalted, melted

## Wet ingredients

2. Whisk wet ingredients in a separate bowl

- milk | 386 grams | 
- egg | 1 | 

## Assembly

Mix wet and dry ingredients together.

Melt some butter in a pan over medium heat.

Scoop 1/4 cup of the batter for each pancake.

Cook pancakes until golden brown.
